Title : 2004–05 Ivy League men's basketball season
Text : The '''2004–05 Ivy League men's basketball season''' was the [[Ivy League]]'s 51st season of basketball. The team with the best record (Penn Quakers) progressed to play in the [[2005 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament]]. It would be their 23rd NCAA tournament appearance. Tim Begley, a senior shooting guard, won the [[Ivy League Men's Basketball Player of the Year]]. He was the eleventh player from the Penn Quakers to win the award.

